{"tid":1781240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十人上街，挪威頒布和平獎給示威者；中共外交部指外國勢力干涉內政。","createTime":"2019-12-13T04:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T05:05:23.000Z","uid":271829,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d66bb426f951fadd0454e5edfc6ae12d6af505be","tid":1781240,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:08:31.000Z","msg":"十人上街，挪威頒布和平獎給示威者；中共外交部指外國勢力干涉內政。<br />\n一百人上街，冰島承諾提前大選；中共聘請五毛在網上分化示威群眾。<br />\n一千人上街，瑞典示威少女成為了時代雜誌年度人物；中共禁網。<br />\n一萬人上街，新西蘭制定應急計劃撤僑；中共進行防暴演習。<br />\n十萬人上街，丹麥政黨容許黨內議員獨立選擇支持哪一方；中共出坦克車屠城。<br />\n一百萬人上街，愛爾蘭進行公投；中共調配航空母艦隊，等待真正的戰爭來臨。<br />\n二百萬人上街，加拿大政府倒台；解放軍抱怨軍備彈藥不夠。<br />\n二百萬零一人上行，芬蘭獨立了；習近平終於說：『好多人反對我們！』<br />\n林鄭：『香港哪些自由民主人權受損？』"},{"pid":"f760813f0d4b9040b02a7efc8cf52b8aa6491f43","tid":1781240,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:11:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1215  和你shop<br />\n1215 社福罷工造勢大會  愛丁堡<br />\n1231 和你拖</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2020 1月1  民陣遊行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjZn7qg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjZn7qg.jpg&h=db134df5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiUzd5h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiUzd5h.jpg&h=510b7bed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eR1hWiD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeR1hWiD.jpg&h=5752bc69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rObYFLj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrObYFLj.png&h=946ca501&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"045156da85b3350d1767f364c1849c6f7ceb43ba","tid":1781240,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:13:52.000Z","msg":"中共係全球毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe5f